Installation
------------

To enable NetworkManager service in NixOS:

       networking.networkmanager.enable = true;

User needs to be in **networkmanager** group in order to control
networkmanager configuration.

### GTK applet

To use **nm-applet**, you have to install **networkmanagerapplet**.

### KDE applet

The Network Manager applet for KDE is in nixpkgs as
**networkmanagement**.

